## LRWRAP
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
https://oracle-base.com/articles/linux/rlwrap

rpm -Uvh https://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/epel-release-latest-7.noarch.rpm
yum install rlwrap
alias sql='rlwrap sqlplus / as sysdba'
oracle@centos8$ sql

